{"tid":1625024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休息唔係驚左緊急法","createTime":"2019-10-05T05:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:50:06.000Z","uid":21220,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2b6bc3a0638499413aab381a7ae2a94b28f65897","tid":1625024,"uid":21220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:37:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母熱門咁多post講休息就係代表驚左矇面法<br />\n話你聽冇人驚呀 最撚驚就係你地開post班弱智仔<br />\n喺到幫人宣傳 搞到好似係真既咁<br />\n唔該咪撚再講乜野驚唔驚<br />\n冇撚人驚呀 冇撚人覺得緊張法有用呀</span>"},{"pid":"baf799561b006f26e7eee13216cc59e5f5903038","tid":1625024,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:38:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3441d192e74ae37488e032145f6fb5e0385e294f","tid":1625024,"uid":172754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:38:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有車人士召集區<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10.5 黨鐵和你塞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4533620b881c821cbee9951710d107392fb2569d","tid":1625024,"uid":36444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"005a2caa1f68c5a07bea6bd7d77c2bcdf5792289","tid":1625024,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:40:05.000Z","msg":"休息係指 討論對策 做貼文宣 宣傳文宣"},{"pid":"20b1fef968384db8ca581d4d1c191398c3fc930c","tid":1625024,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:41:31.000Z","msg":"大家記住，今日唔遊行唔等於係屋企休息啊，係要全民做文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624535</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6f712d572dd246b39c1177d90b1eb69f02adbc4d","tid":1625024,"uid":21220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:42:49.000Z","msg":